      "subtopic": "Phishing and Social Engineering Attacks",
      "question": "A fraud examiner is investigating a case where employees at ABC Corporation received emails appearing to be from their IT department, requesting they click a link to verify their credentials. Several employees complied, and their login information was subsequently used to access the company's financial system and initiate unauthorized wire transfers totaling $250,000. The perpetrator created a fake website that mimicked the company's legitimate login page. Which of the following BEST describes this type of cyberfraud scheme?",
