      "question": "A fraud examiner is investigating a case where an employee received an email appearing to be from the company's CEO requesting immediate wire transfer of funds to a new vendor account. The email address was slightly misspelled and the transfer was completed before verification. What type of cyberfraud scheme is this, and what preventive control would be most effective?",
