      "question": "A fraudster sends emails to employees of XYZ Corporation pretending to be the company's IT department, requesting that recipients click a link and enter their login credentials to \"verify their accounts.\" Several employees comply, and the fraudster uses the stolen credentials to access the company's internal systems and steal customer data. Which of the following BEST describes this type of cyberfraud scheme?",
